---
import Mark from './Mark.astro';
---
<section class="blk" id="about" style="background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
  <div class="wrap about">
    <div class="body reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n="about.eyebrow">About</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,46px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.035em;font-weight:800;margin:14px 0 26px" data-i18n="about.h2">
        A small studio that ships like a big one.
      </h2>
      <p data-i18n-html="about.p1">
        <b>CodeDMark</b> is a software studio out of Thailand. The name is a promise that works
        in two languages: in English it reads as a developer's mark on the work; in Thai,
        <b>โค้ดดีมาก</b> — "code that's very good."
      </p>
      <p data-i18n-html="about.p2">
        We come from embedded — where a bug means a field return, not a hotfix — so testing
        isn't a phase, it's a habit. That discipline travels with us up the stack to mobile and web.
      </p>
      <p data-i18n-html="about.p3">
        Founded by <b>Bancha Rajainthong</b>. We take on a small number of engagements at a time,
        so the people who scope your project are the ones who build it.
      </p>
      <div class="pills">
        <span data-i18n="about.tested">Tested</span>
        <span data-i18n="about.shipped">Shipped</span>
        <span data-i18n="about.measured">Measured</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-id reveal">
      <div class="top">
        <Mark size={54} />
        <div>
          <div class="nm">CodeDMark<span class="dot">.</span></div>
          <div class="ro">Software studio · est. Thailand</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rows">
        <div class="r">
          <span class="k" data-i18n="about.entity">Entity</span>
          <span class="v th">บริษัท โค้ดดีมาก จำกัด</span>
        </div>
        <div class="r">
          <span class="k" data-i18n="about.registered">Registered</span>
          <span class="v">CODEDMARK Co., Ltd.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="r">
          <span class="k" data-i18n="about.focus">Focus</span>
          <span class="v">Embedded · Mobile · Web</span>
        </div>
        <div class="r">
          <span class="k">Email</span>
          <span class="v">eswizardry@gmail.com</span>
        </div>
        <div class="r">
          <span class="k">GitHub</span>
          <span class="v">github.com/eswizardry</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
